      <workgroup>Internet Area Working Group</workgroup>
      <keyword>port logging</keyword>
      <abstract>
        <t>&lt;p&gt;In the wake of IPv4 exhaustion and deployment of IP address sharing techniques, this document recommends that Internet-facing servers log port number and accurate timestamps in addition to the incoming IP address.  This memo documents an Internet Best Current Practice.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
